      "content": "helplines dont help. they just tell u to take deep breaths or whatever and then the notifications just keep coming. it won't stop. it feels like there's no way out, like no matter what i do the world is just gonna keep hitting me. i'm just so tired of it all. what's even the point of trying to fix things when everything is already ruined?",
