      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the noise though. it's the feeling that everyone saw what happened and they're all just judging me or laughing. i look at my future and i just see more of this. more people being mean, more feeling like a freak. it feels like the only way to actually find peace and just be still is to... i don't know. like, to just stop existing. does that even make sense? like, if i wasn't here, the cruelty wouldn't be able to reach me anymore.",
